description: Use this operation to copy results of a Vector Enrichment job to an Amazon S3 location.

parameters.name: Arn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the Vector Enrichment job.

parameters.name: ClientToken
parameters.description: A unique token that guarantees that the call to this API is idempotent. This field is autopopulated if not provided.

parameters.name: ExecutionRoleArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the IAM rolewith permission to upload to the location in OutputConfig.

parameters.name: OutputConfig
parameters.description: Output location information for exporting Vector Enrichment Job results. The input structure for Amazon S3 data; representing the Amazon S3 location of the input data objects. KmsKeyId (string) --- The Key Management Service key ID for server-side encryption. The URL to the Amazon S3 data for the Vector Enrichment job.

nested_params.name: S3Data
nested_params.description: The input structure for Amazon S3 data; representing the Amazon S3 location of the input data objects.

nested_params.name: KmsKeyId
nested_params.description: The Key Management Service key ID for server-side encryption.

nested_params.name: S3Uri
nested_params.description: The URL to the Amazon S3 data for the Vector Enrichment job.
